mil.emp3.api.listeners

Interface IEventListener<T extends IEvent>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - An object the is derived from IEvent.

    See the package overview for more information.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICameraEventListener, IContainerEventListener, IFeatureDrawEventListener, IFeatureEditEventListener, IFeatureEventListener, IFeatureInteractionEventListener, ILookAtEventListener, IMapFeatureAddedEventListener, IMapFeatureRemovedEventListener, IMapFreehandEventListener, IMapInteractionEventListener, IMapStateChangeEventListener, IMapViewChangeEventListener, IVisibilityEventListener

    public interface IEventListener<T extends IEvent>
    This interface defines the base of all event listener interfaces.
